title: Top 30 Country May 20, 2014
description:
Rewind by Rascal Flatts is not only their 33rd single release but also their newest number one country single as of May 20, 2014.  The new song by Dierks Bentley (Drunk On A Plane) is the only debut, while Bottoms Up slides down the chart to become a recurrent.  It is also worthy of note that Luke Bryan can be heard both in the number 2 and 3 positions of this weeks chart, as a guest and on his own. 

Here are the Top 30 U.S. Country singles for the week as ranked by Mediabase.  All are 320 constant bit-rate Stereo and ripped from either ERGÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Nu Country Traxx, Promo Only Country Radio, the iTunes single or the actual artist CD.  Have a great week!
